{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idb6cfdda4-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300hh–13"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"300hh–13"},"text":"§ 300hh–13.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Evaluation of new and emerging technologies regarding bioterrorist attack and other public health emergencies","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb6cfdda5-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300hh–13/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of Health and Human Services (referred to in this section as the “Secretary”) shall promptly carry out a program to periodically evaluate new and emerging technologies that, in the determination of the Secretary, are designed to improve or enhance the ability of public health or safety officials to conduct public health surveillance activities relating to a bioterrorist attack or other public health emergency.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb6cfdda6-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300hh–13/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Certain activities","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In carrying out this subsection, the Secretary shall, to the extent practicable—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb6cfdda7-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300hh–13/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" survey existing technology programs funded by the Federal Government for potentially useful technologies;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb6cfdda8-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300hh–13/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" promptly issue a request, as necessary, for information from non-Federal public and private entities for ongoing activities in this area; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb6cfdda9-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300hh–13/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" evaluate technologies identified under paragraphs (1) and (2) pursuant to subsection (c).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb6cfddaa-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300hh–13/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Consultation and evaluation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In carrying out subsection (b)(3), the Secretary shall consult with the working group under section 247d–6(a) ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002508"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002508"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" of this title, as well as other appropriate public, nonprofit, and private entities, to develop criteria for the evaluation of such technologies and to conduct such evaluations."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb6cfddab-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300hh–13/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Report","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Not later than 180 days after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-06-12"},"text":"June 12, 2002","children":[],"tail":", and periodically thereafter, the Secretary shall submit to the Committee on Energy and Commerce of the House of Representatives, and the Committee on Health, Education, Labor, and Pensions of the Senate, a report on the activities under this section."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idb6cfddac-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/188/tI/s126"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–188, title I, § 126","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-06-12"},"text":"June 12, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/116/615"},"text":"116 Stat. 615","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idb6cfddad-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idb6cfddae-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idb6cfddaf-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s247d–6"},"text":"Section 247d–6 of this title","children":[],"tail":", referred to in subsec. (c), was amended by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/417/tIII/s304"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–417, title III, § 304","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2006-12-19"},"text":"Dec. 19, 2006","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/120/2859"},"text":"120 Stat. 2859","children":[],"tail":", and as so amended, subsec. (a) of section 247d–6 no longer relates to a working group."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idb6cfddb0-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was enacted as part of the Public Health Security and Bioterrorism Preparedness and Response Act of 2002, and not as part of the Public Health Service Act which comprises this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
